---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="Privacy Policy — Derin Okuma" description="Privacy Policy for Derin Okuma" />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />

		<main class="about-page">
			<section class="about-hero">
				<p class="about-eyebrow">Legal</p>
				<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
				<p class="about-lead">
					This policy explains what data Derin Okuma collects and how it is used.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="about-section">
				<h2>Overview</h2>
				<p>
					Derin Okuma is a creator-operated website. The site itself does not collect personal
					data from visitors. There are no user accounts, no tracking pixels, and no
					advertising systems on this website.
				</p>
				<p>
					The site operator uses an internal publishing tool that connects to the TikTok API
					to upload short-form videos as drafts. This document describes how that integration
					handles data.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="about-section">
				<h2>TikTok Integration</h2>
				<p>
					The TikTok API integration is used exclusively by the site's creator (operator) to
					automate draft video uploads. It is not a public-facing product.
				</p>
				<ul>
					<li>
						<strong>OAuth authorization:</strong> The tool uses TikTok's OAuth 2.0 flow to
						obtain authorization to upload videos. The requested API scope is
						<code>video.upload</code>.
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Token storage:</strong> OAuth access tokens received from TikTok are
						stored locally on the operator's machine or in a private secrets store. Tokens
						are never committed to the public repository and are not shared with any
						third party.
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Data use:</strong> TikTok account data accessed via the API is used
						solely for the purpose of uploading draft videos. It is not used for advertising,
						analytics, profiling, or any other purpose.
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Data sharing:</strong> TikTok user data is not sold, rented, or shared
						with third parties, except as strictly necessary to interact with TikTok's
						official API endpoints.
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Data retention:</strong> No TikTok user data is stored beyond what is
						transiently necessary to complete an upload request.
					</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="about-section">
				<h2>Website Visitors</h2>
				<p>
					The Derin Okuma website (derin-okuma.vercel.app) is a static Astro site hosted on
					Vercel. Vercel may collect standard server logs (IP address, browser type, page
					visited) as part of normal hosting operations. Please refer to
					<a href="https://vercel.com/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
						Vercel's Privacy Policy
					</a>
					for details.
				</p>
				<p>
					Derin Okuma does not install cookies, does not use analytics services, and does not
					collect any personally identifiable information from website visitors.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="about-section">
				<h2>Revoking TikTok Access</h2>
				<p>
					If you have authorized Derin Okuma's TikTok integration (as the operator), you can
					revoke access at any time from your TikTok account settings under
					<strong>Security &gt; Apps and Websites</strong>.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="about-section">
				<h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
				<p>
					This privacy policy may be updated from time to time. The date at the bottom of
					this page reflects when it was last revised.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="about-section">
				<h2>Contact</h2>
				<p>
					For questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact:
					<a href="mailto:derinokumaofficial@gmail.com">derinokumaofficial@gmail.com</a>
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="about-note">
				<p>Last updated: May 2026</p>
			</section>
		</main>

		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
